Selena, Renata and Ana are three inseparable friends. From small share everything: stories, adventures and swearing that no man will ever separate them. This year, they will have fun at the famous shores of Praia Brava. For 10 days experience passions, pleasures and freedoms that they had never imagined living. Between games, laughter and bonfires by the sea, known to his friends Marcio and three local boys who engage an enigmatic seduction. The holidays are going wild and each episode feels more intense experience than the last. Relaxed and fun, the three friends become involved in very hot where they unleash all their fantasies. An unforgettable summer in which discover they do not know as much as they thought and that oaths, many times, leads the rolling waves.
